name: Aptek速 2312-Pmf
description: Aptek速 2312-Pmf is a one component, premixed-frozen, silver filled, electrically conductive soft paste adhesive. It is designed to bond many dissimilar substrates and dissipate device generated heat. Aptek速 2312-Pmf is a 100% solids, solvent free system that will not form voids during cure or outgas after being fully cured.
